Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九尾查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照路顶呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说会丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有两面性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然鸣人能使用九尾查克拉模式了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并不代表他和九尾搞好了关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人的查克拉仍然会被九尾吸走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦查克拉清零 鸣人就会死…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人此刻很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止激情太过分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用九尾查克拉当手电筒确实不错…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟丢了 跟紧了 蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.82,0:01:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.03,0:01:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是毫不客气地消费我的查克拉啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在你体内看着你的一举一动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是那么天真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争就让我来终结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憎恨也好 痛苦也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部由我来承担
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了我的查克拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骨瘦如柴的你变回原样一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…还真是少见啊 九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然会主动跟我搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你耐不住寂寞想找人倾诉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我现在正忙着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后再听你说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的认为仅凭一己之力就能结束战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你多少也感觉到敌人的规模有多庞大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且斑也在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道他会设下什么圈套哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我就将力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再吃你那套了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:03:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你变机灵了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…你早就露出马脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有话战争结束后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果同伴被杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仇恨随之便会诞生…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能在事态演变成那样之前消灭所有敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒敌人就会被他们憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的想自己背负一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别总是小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别总是小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真能消除大家的仇恨并背负一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该出现了很多战死者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也孕育出了仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经在你身边的佐助就是为仇恨所困
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对他不是毫无办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天起 你就应该察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会跟谁对战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是哪个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗帽子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风帽墨镜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太想和朋友打架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是那么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是传统的忍者对练
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历代的火影们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是通过忍者对练以提升实力的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出界了 就算我输吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换后面的继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是训练还是别的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是为了分个胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就赶紧决定输赢好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么麻烦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真没志气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一辈子也当不上中忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那可不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要问为何的话 一生很漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期间会有很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别钻牛角尖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:08:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 鹿丸那家伙才是最麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次也毫无斗志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井野 你认识他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧 父母的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸 丁次 结和解之印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不擅长这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完成和解之印了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈不让我跟他说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想和他交手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是 宇智波佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩都给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和佐助结和解之印啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把对手打得落花流水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙怎么回事 就会装酷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…打败这个受欢迎的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能备受瞩目了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 我绝对不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油…鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就是漩涡鸣人对宇智波佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有本事就来吧 拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在对决前用惯用手和对方结下对立之印
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是礼仪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事随便啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧让我放倒这家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在起 我就要人气爆棚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如你所愿立刻让你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者对练是一直恪守的传统训练方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有些形式化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但忍者学校必须从基础教起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在对决之前 一定要单手结印 面向对方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是双手结印发动忍术动作的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表示即将进入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是对立之印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在对决结束 分出胜负之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双方伸出对立之印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相互钩在一起 结成和解之印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而表达出依然是伙伴的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止就是忍者对练的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有在听吗 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说第二遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“好”只要说一次就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害 好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家平时看我的眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…比那更强烈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…他没在看我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双方结下和解之印
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换下一组
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本就当我不存在吗 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 是狗屎 狗屎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬邦邦稀稀一大坨的混蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙连骂人都不会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是便秘还是拉肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望他分清楚些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要问为何的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说别钻牛角尖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒说两句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗屎 硬邦邦稀稀一大坨的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说忍者对练是神圣的传统了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧给我结和解之印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想打吗 拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个 适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真差劲 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后呢…佐助变成什么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将他的仇恨消除了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有 与此相反
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该清醒点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既没有父母 也没有兄弟的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能理解我什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就孤身一人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底能理解我什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在无论你说什么 我都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会将你和村里的所有人都杀得一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的只有那条路可以走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终你的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么杀了我成为守护村子的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么被我干掉 成为一条丧家之犬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的仇恨反而越来越强烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身边最亲近的同伴都这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 不管是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都无法消除仇恨 也无法承担仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…说完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我就该惧怕退缩 无动于衷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样不就如你所愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天真的是你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连一个佐助都救不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还如此狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果连自己的决定都不相信 那就真完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会设法帮助佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设法解决这场战争的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又想封印我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是那种小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你寄住在我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就给点租金 借些查克拉给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超大玉…螺旋多连丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股力量是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…这是九尾的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…惹毛我了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这么大的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然很厉害啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是六道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我记住了 鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当年的小鬼变得相当能说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望有一天也能把你的憎恨给消除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你让我痛苦不堪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道被憎恨支配的滋味不好受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是九尾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没沦落到被你这臭小鬼拯救的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是憎恨的集合体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这反而更有拯救的价值了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我的确太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就像老爸老妈曾在我体内一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一直与我相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的想法和成长你都能了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你也许不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你一直都在注视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…你就继续留在那里关注我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助…你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你的眼中从未有过我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我…一直都在关注着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 佐助也好 战争也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光芒四射的鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月下严峻的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加轻松地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又和九尾吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尾兽模式是和九尾进行的查克拉拔河比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有查克拉 生命就落幕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以别乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道自己有点乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一向言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的忍道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经帮你包扎好外伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你趁现在好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.57,0:22:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.68,0:22:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说医疗忍者接二连三被人暗杀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次…. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得你会如此消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为看不见的敌人不知道隐藏在何处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集「火影忍者 疾风传」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「被狙击的医疗忍者」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.36,0:22:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 必须要小心了
